Revv52 Engagement Survey 2026

[Estimated completion time: 15 - 20 minutes]

  

Thank you for taking the time to complete this survey. Your feedback plays an important role in shaping the future of Revv52 and helping us continue to build a strong, welcoming, and high-calibre musical community.

We genuinely value honest and thoughtful responses from everyone who has been part of Revv52 — whether you are currently active, on hiatus, or have recently stepped away from the group. Your experiences and perspectives matter to us, and we hope you will feel comfortable sharing them openly, whether they relate to this most recent show or to any past experience with the ensemble. If you are commenting on a different season/show, please indicate that in the optional notes section.

Please don’t feel pressured to answer every question. Some topics may not reflect your experience or concerns, and that is completely okay. We would much rather receive meaningful, detailed responses to the questions that matter most to you than brief answers that provide little insight.

All responses will remain anonymous. Thank you again for helping us learn, grow, and strengthen the Revv52 community for everyone involved.

  

